## Tables

| Feature | Markdown | MarkNext |
|--------:|:--------:|:--------:|
| Bold Syntax | 2 ways | 1 way |
| Italic Syntax | 2 ways | 1 way |
| Headers | 2 styles | 1 style |
| Security | Vulnerable | Safe |

## Extensions (Safe Shortcodes)

[warning text="This is an important warning message"]

[alert type="tip" text="Use MarkNext for safer documentation"]

[^1]: This is a footnote. Footnotes are processed at compile time.

Math can be included with extensions: $E = mc^2$

## Escaping

To show literal syntax characters, escape them:

- \*not bold\*
- \/not italic\/
- \`not code\`
- \[not a link\]

## Line Breaks

This is line one\
And this is line two (forced break with backslash)

---

That's the end of this example!
